        "id": 2402518,
        "name": "Nathan Smyth",
        "username": "Nathan_Smyth",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/8c91f0/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-04-23T03:16:41.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think some of us must not have the correct tastebuds for the CLN.</p>\n<p>I never really understood the wine, whereas my Mom thinks the CLN is the best wine she\u2019s ever tasted.</p>\n<p>Another suspicion I have is that the CLN improves significantly after five to ten years in the bottle, and that you really need to be patient with it.</p>",
