        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/8c91f0/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-04-23T03:19:01.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My opinion of Vatan is kinda the same as [although exactly the opposite of] my opinion of Texier: With Texier, everyone raves about his reds, but actually his whites are his best wines; and with Vatan, everyone raves about the CLN when in fact his Pinot Noir was his best wine.</p>",
